publictruefalse1352af89db2d9340bea7ff561d9619f89b38442ddb721300bea7ff561d9619f8Add Recipient to Envelope<p>This action adds a recipient to an envelope on DocuSign. Prior to using this action, Create Draft Envelope from Template action will be used to generate a draft Envelope.</p> <p><b>Inputs:</b></p> <ul> <li><b>Envelope</b> - The envelope record that has the envelope ID.</li> <li><b>Email</b> - Email ID of the recipient.</li> <li><b>Name</b> - Name of the recipient.</li> <li><b>Role Name</b> - Role Name from the envelope to which the recipient is to be associated.</li> <li><b>Recipient ID</b> - Recipient ID from the envelope to which the recipient is to be associated.</li> <li><b>Embedded Signing Recipient</b> - Select or drag and drop the ServiceNow user record to be used for embedded signing. The Email Address ,User Name and User ID fields are extracted from the user record and used for embedded signing. Ensure that the Use Embedded Signing checkbox is checked when using this field.</li> </ul> <p><b>Outputs:</b></p> <ul> <li><b>Status</b> - Will be set to "Success" if the request succeeds or "Error" if a failure occurs.</li> <li><b>Error Message</b> - Will be populated when the status is "Error".</li> </ul> <p><b>Error Messages:</b></p> <ul> <li>The specified Integrator Key was not found or is disabled. Please verify the configured credentials.</li> <li>User lacks sufficient permission to perform this action.</li> <li>Provided recipient ID is invalid or does not exist.</li> <li>The email address for the recipient is invalid or is of incorrect format.</li> <li>User Record is not provided or the User Record is missing either the name, email or user ID.</li> <li>Either Email or Name has not been provided.</li> </ul> <p>To use this action, the corresponding DocuSign connection and credential must be created and associated with the DocuSign Connection & Credential alias.</p> <p><b>Additional Note:</b></p> <ul> <li>Requires a subscription to a DocuSign API Plan that satisfies your feature and transactions requirements. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.docusign.com/products-and-pricing/api-plans">Read More</a>.</li> </ul> <p>To use this action, the corresponding DocuSign connection and credential must be created and associated with the DocuSign Connection & Credential alias. <a target="_blank" href="http://docs.servicenow.com/?context=CSHelp:credentials-connections-alias">Learn More</a></p> <p><b>Note</b>: Requires a subscription for production use. <a target="_blank" href="https://docs.servicenow.com/?context=CSHelp:IntegrationHub-licensing-information">Read More</a>.</p> &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sub-flow Inputs:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Account&lt;/b&gt; - The account record that contains DocuSign account and connection alias information.&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sub-flow Steps:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;(Action)Get Templates Per Account&lt;/b&gt;: This action retrieves templates corresponding to Account.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Error messages are logged using log action in case of failures while retrieving account or templates details. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Additional Notes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;User must have connection and credential aliases created under DocuSign Spoke.&lt;/li&gt;
       &lt;li&gt;Requires a subscription to a DocuSign API Plan that satisfies your feature and transactions requirements. &lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://www.docusign.com/products-and-pricing/api-plans&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note&lt;/b&gt;: Requires a subscription for production use. &lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000407</definition_id><description>Average transactions in last 12 months for all scopes</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>outbound_usage_metrics_avg_all</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var aggregator = new OutboundUsageMetricsAggregator();
var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', false);
var totalSum = 0;
while (sums.next()) {  
  totalSum = totalSum + parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'agg_value'), 10);
}
answer = totalSum/12;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-08-17 00:10:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>45892e36e7a0030007a64caac2f6a9d7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000407</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_45892e36e7a0030007a64caac2f6a9d7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-25 14:41:02</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000367</definition_id><description>Orchestration Core transactions only executed in the last 30 days (Does not include today)</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>OrchCoreTransactionLast30Days</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>true</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Daily</schedule><script><![CDATA[var count = new global.OrchCoreTransactionQuery().getTransactionsCount("sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.daysAgoStart(30)@javascript:gs.daysAgoEnd(1)");

// get SAMP TX and substract SAMP TX 
var sampCount = new global.SAMPTXCounter().getReclamationTXCountForLast30Days();
count = count - sampCount;  

answer = count;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-04-28 20:50:43</sys_created_on><sys_id>a13dd75f2f5232009ac402d3c18c954d</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000367</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_a13dd75f2f5232009ac402d3c18c954d</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000368</definition_id><description>In the last 12 months, The highest Orchestration Core only transactions executed in a given month</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>MaxOrchCoreTransactionLast12Month</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>true</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxCnt=0;
// Last 12 months
var queryString = "sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(12)@javascript:gs.endOfLastMonth()";
var monthlyTrend = new global.OrchCoreTransactionQuery().getTransactionsCountMonthlyTrend(queryString);

for(var i=0; i<monthlyTrend.length; i++){
	var monthlyCount = monthlyTrend[i].count;
	var month = monthlyTrend[i].month;
	var monthlyQueryString = "sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(" + month + ")@javascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(" + month-1 + ")";
	var sampCnt = new global.SAMPTXCounter().getReclamationTXCount(monthlyQueryString);
	monthlyCount = monthlyCount - sampCnt;
	if (monthlyCount > maxCnt)
		maxCnt = monthlyCount;
}
answer = maxCnt;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-04-25 21:32:05</sys_created_on><sys_id>96e94ce22f5e32009ac402d3c18c952b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>19</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000368</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_96e94ce22f5e32009ac402d3c18c952b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.RemoveColumnPrefix</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>RemoveColumnPrefix</name><script><![CDATA[var RemoveColumnPrefix = Class.create();
RemoveColumnPrefix.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
copyFields : function (source_table, target_table, extends_table) {
    var tgr = new GlideRecord(target_table);
    tgr.initialize();

    var attrs = new Packages.java.util.HashMap();

    var fields = tgr.getFields();
    for (var i = 0; i < fields.size(); i++) {
      var field = fields.get(i);
      var type = field.getED().getInternalType();
      var fname = field.getName();
      if (fname.startsWith('sys_'))
        continue;

      var dgr2 = new GlideRecord("sys_dictionary");
      dgr2.addQuery("name", source_table);
      dgr2.addQuery("element", fname);
      dgr2.query();
      if (!dgr2.next()) {
        if(fname.indexOf('u_') != 0)
		  fname = 'u_' + fname;

        var ca = new GlideColumnAttributes(fname);
        ca.setType("string");
        ca.setUsePrefix(false);
        attrs.put(fname, ca);
      }
    }

    var tc = new GlideTableCreator(source_table, source_table);
    tc.setColumnAttributes(attrs);
    if(typeof extends_table != 'undefined')
      	tc.setExtends(extends_table);
    tc.setOverrideUpdate(true);
    tc.update();
  },
    type: 'RemoveColumnPrefix'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-08-19 14:38:50</sys_created_on><sys_id>31b31ba6db1333000510196c299619ef</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>RemoveColumnPrefix</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_31b31ba6db1333000510196c299619ef</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-08-19 14:38:50</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000364</definition_id><description>In the last 12 months, The highest Orchestration transactions executed in a given month</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>MaxAllOrchTransactionLast12Month</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>true</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxCnt = 0; 
var exeGr = new GlideAggregate("orch_execution");  
exeGr.addTrend("sys_created_on","Month");  
exeGr.addAggregate("COUNT");  
exeGr.addEncodedQuery("sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(12)@javascript:gs.endOfLastMonth()");
exeGr.query();  
while(exeGr.next()) {  
  var currentCnt = parseInt(exeGr.getAggregate("COUNT"));
  if (currentCnt > maxCnt)
          maxCnt = currentCnt;  
}

answer = maxCnt;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-03-24 22:17:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>ef71e7cc2f3132003a8a02d3c18c9508</sys_id><sys_mod_count>19</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000364</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_ef71e7cc2f3132003a8a02d3c18c9508</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_c66e7bbab3020300176b051a16a8dc5e
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000420</definition_id><description>In the last 12 months, the highest Orchestration Core and IntegrationHub transactions executed in a given month</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>1</license_model><name>MaxOrchAndIntegrationHubTransactionsLast12Month</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[function getOrchMaxCount(){
	var maxCnt=0;
	if(GlidePluginManager.isActive('com.snc.runbook_automation.runtime')) {
		// Last 12 months
		var queryString = "sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(12)@javascript:gs.endOfLastMonth()";
		var monthlyTrend = new global.OrchCoreTransactionQuery().getTransactionsCountMonthlyTrend(queryString);
		
		for(var i=0; i<monthlyTrend.length; i++){
			var monthlyCount = monthlyTrend[i].count;
			var month = monthlyTrend[i].month;
			var monthlyQueryString = "sys_created_onBETWEENjavascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(" + month + ")@javascript:gs.monthsAgoStart(" + month-1 + ")";
			var sampCnt = new global.SAMPTXCounter().getReclamationTXCount(monthlyQueryString);
			monthlyCount = monthlyCount - sampCnt;
			if (monthlyCount > maxCnt)
				maxCnt = monthlyCount;
		}
	}
	return maxCnt;
}

function getIHMaxCount(){
	var aggregator = new OutboundUsageMetricsAggregator();
	var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', true);
	var maxCount = 0;
	while (sums.next()) {
		var currentCount = parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'agg_value'));
		if(currentCount > maxCount)
			maxCount = currentCount;
	}
	return maxCount;
}
answer = getOrchMaxCount()+getIHMaxCount();]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-10-30 20:00:06</sys_created_on><sys_id>c66e7bbab3020300176b051a16a8dc5e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000420</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_c66e7bbab3020300176b051a16a8dc5e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-25 14:41:02</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000260</definition_id><description>Max number of shares for any console</description><exec_time_threshold>3000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>max_number_of_shares_for_any_console</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxShares = 0;

var ga = new GlideAggregate('planned_task_custom_console_member');
ga.groupBy('console');
ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
ga.query();

while(ga.next()) {
	if(parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT')) > maxShares) {
		maxShares = parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT'));
	}
}

answer = maxShares;
]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-02-28 10:31:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>ec6815980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a3f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000260</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_ec6815980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a3f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000421</definition_id><description>Orchestration Core and IntegrationHub transactions executed in last month</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>1</license_model><name>OrchAndIntegrationHubTransactionsLastMonth</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[// Orchestration Transactions LastMonth
var orchTxLastMonth = 0;
if(GlidePluginManager.isActive('com.snc.runbook_automation.runtime')) {
	orchTxLastMonth = new global.OrchCoreTransactionQuery().getTransactionsCount("sys_created_onONLast month@javascript:gs.beginningOfLastMonth()@javascript:gs.endOfLastMonth()");
	// get SAMP TX and substract SAMP TX 
	var sampCount = new global.SAMPTXCounter().getReclamationTXCountForLastMonth();
	orchTxLastMonth = orchTxLastMonth - sampCount;
} 
// IntegrationHub Transaction LastMonth
var ihTxLastMonth = new OutboundUsageMetricsAggregator().getTransactionCountForLastMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', true);

answer = orchTxLastMonth+ihTxLastMonth;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-10-30 20:08:48</sys_created_on><sys_id>67b180cbb3020300176b051a16a8dca4</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000421</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_67b180cbb3020300176b051a16a8dca4</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-25 14:41:02</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: usageanalytics_count_cfg_b975742dcb012200467d3682634c9c03
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000212</definition_id><description>Number of Orchestration activities developed or modified by a customer</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>CustomActivitiesDeveloped</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>true</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Daily</schedule><script><![CDATA[var constants = Object.freeze({
    "wad": 'wf_activity_definition' ,
    "wea": 'wf_element_activity'
});

function getOrchActivitiesTouchedByCustomer() {
	var ga = new GlideAggregate('sys_update_xml');
	ga.addQuery('name', 'STARTSWITH', constants.wad).addOrCondition('name', 'STARTSWITH', constants.wea);
	ga.groupBy('name');
	ga.query();
	var listOfLegacySysIds = [] ;
	var listOfElementSysIds = [] ;
	while(ga.next()) {	
		if(ga.name.startsWith(constants.wad)) {
			listOfLegacySysIds.push(ga.name.substring(constants.wad.length + 1));
		} else {
			listOfElementSysIds.push(ga.name.substring(constants.wea.length + 1));
		}
	}
	return getLegacyCount(listOfLegacySysIds) + getElementCount(listOfElementSysIds);
}

function getLegacyCount(listOfLegacySysIds) {
	var listOfNonOrchPackageNames = ['Workflow Runtime Engine', 'Service Catalog Platform', 'Service Creator'];
	var ga = new GlideAggregate(constants.wad);
	ga.addQuery('sys_id', 'IN', listOfLegacySysIds);
	ga.addQuery('sys_package.name', 'NOT IN', listOfNonOrchPackageNames);
	ga.query();
	var legacyActivityCount = ga.getRowCount();
	gs.info("Legacy Activity Count: " + legacyActivityCount);
	return legacyActivityCount;
}

function getElementCount(listOfElementSysIds) {
	var ga = new GlideAggregate(constants.wea);
	ga.addQuery('sys_id', 'IN', listOfElementSysIds);
	ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
	ga.addAggregate('count(distinct','version_container_id');
	ga.query();
	var elementActivityCount = ga.getRowCount();
	gs.info("Element Activity Count: " + elementActivityCount);
	return elementActivityCount;
}

var start = new Date().getTime();
var finalActivityCount = getOrchActivitiesTouchedByCustomer();
var end = new Date().getTime();
gs.info("Total time taken: " + (end - start) + " ms");
gs.info('Final Count:' + finalActivityCount);

answer = finalActivityCount;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-08-04 22:44:29</sys_created_on><sys_id>b975742dcb012200467d3682634c9c03</sys_id><sys_mod_count>10</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000212</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_b975742dcb012200467d3682634c9c03</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sysevent_script_action"><sysevent_script_action action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><condition_script/><description/><event_name>login.failed</event_name><name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</name><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[//
// Check to see if the user has failed to login too many times
// when the limit is reached, lock the user out of the system.
// Also create a trigger to unlock the user after 'N' minutes.
//

lockoutOnFailedLogin();

function lockoutOnFailedLogin() {
	var maxUnlockAttempts = gs.getProperty("glide.user.max_unlock_attempts", 5);
	var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
	if (gr.get("user_name", event.parm1.toString())) {
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts)
			return;

		gr.failed_attempts += 1;
		if (gr.failed_attempts > maxUnlockAttempts) {
			gr.locked_out = true;
			gr.update();
			gs.log("User " + event.parm1 + " locked out due to too many invalid login attempts");
			triggerUnlock(gr.sys_id);
		} else {
			gr.update();       
		}
	}
}

function triggerUnlock(userSysID) {
	var unlockIn = gs.getProperty("glide.user.unlock_timeout_in_mins", 15);
	var trigger = new GlideRecord("sys_trigger");
	trigger.name = "Unlock the user after "+ unlockIn + " mins";
	trigger.next_action = getTriggerTime(unlockIn);
	trigger.job_id.setDisplayValue('RunScriptJob');
	trigger.script = getTriggerScript(userSysID);
	trigger.document = 'sys_user';
	trigger.document_key = userSysID;
	trigger.state = 0;
	trigger.trigger_type = 0;
	trigger.insert();
}

function getTriggerScript(userSysID) {
	var ret = ""
	+ "var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('sys_id', '" +userSysID+ "');\n"
	+ "gr.addQuery('locked_out', true);\n"
	+ "gr.query();\n"
	+ "if (gr.next()) {\n"
		+ "gr.locked_out = false;\n"
		+ "gr.failed_attempts = 0;\n"
		+ "gr.update();\n"
		+ "gs.log('Auto-unlocking user '+gr.name);\n"
	+ "} else {\n"
		+ "gs.log('Unable to auto-unlock user with sys_id: "+userSysID+"');\n"
	+ "}";
	return ret;
}

function getTriggerTime(minutesToAdd) {
	var checkTime = new GlideDateTime(/*now*/);
	checkTime.addSeconds(minutesToAdd * 60);
	return checkTime;
}
]]></script><synchronous>true</synchronous><sys_class_name>sysevent_script_action</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2013-08-24 00:27:47</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SNC User Lockout Check with Auto Unlock</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="High Security Settings" source="com.glide.high_security">0fcc913874e0330078509adcc48c8758</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysevent_script_action_d92636b2975301008e00958e3b297567</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-24 16:53:31</sys_updated_on></sysevent_script_action></record_update>

	var query = current.getEncodedQuery();
	if (query.indexOf('agent') != -1) {
		var agent = '';
		var queryArr = query.split('^');
		for (var i = 0; i < queryArr.length; i++)
			if (queryArr[i].indexOf('agent') != -1)
				agent = queryArr[i].split('=')[1];
		
		var mid = MIDServer.getByName(agent);

		if (mid && mid.isPreGeneva())
			current.addQuery('topic', 'IN', ['SystemCommand', 'HeartbeatProbe']);
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>will.swift</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-03-03 23:49:05</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MID Server" source="com.glideapp.agent">43fb9d7074e0330078509adcc48c87f6</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-24 16:35:00</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000261</definition_id><description>Max custom console configurations for any user</description><exec_time_threshold>3000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>max_custom_console_configurations_for_any_user</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var maxConfigs = 0;

var ga = new GlideAggregate('planned_task_custom_console');
ga.groupBy('owner');
ga.addAggregate('COUNT');
ga.query();

while(ga.next()) {
	if(parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT')) > maxConfigs) {
		maxConfigs = parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT'));
	}
}

answer = maxConfigs;
]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-02-28 10:21:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>372711980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a0f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000261</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_372711980bd13200b7d0c32c15673a0f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Inputs:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Envelope &lt;/b&gt; - The envelope record that contains account, envelope id.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Target Prior to using this action, Create Draft Envelope from Template action will be used to generate a draft Envelope.&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Inputs:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Envelope&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - The envelope record that has the envelope ID.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Email&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Email ID of the recipient.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Name&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Name of the recipient.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Role Name&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Role Name from the envelope to which the recipient is to be associated.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Recipient ID&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Recipient ID from the envelope to which the recipient is to be associated.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Embedded Signing Recipient&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Select or drag and drop the ServiceNow user record to be used for embedded signing. The Email Address ,User Name and User ID fields are extracted from the user record and used for embedded signing. Ensure that the Use Embedded Signing checkbox is checked when using this field.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Outputs:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Status&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Will be set to &amp;amp;quot;Success&amp;amp;quot; if the request succeeds or &amp;amp;quot;Error&amp;amp;quot; if a failure occurs.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Error Message&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt; - Will be populated when the status is &amp;amp;quot;Error&amp;amp;quot;.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Error Messages:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;The specified Integrator Key was not found or is disabled. Please verify the configured credentials.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;User lacks sufficient permission to perform this action.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Provided recipient ID is invalid or does not exist.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt; &amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;The email address for the recipient is invalid or is of incorrect sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEFN1000501</definition_id><description>Returns a JSON with number of total conversations and conversations per conversation states</description><exec_time_threshold>200</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>ConversationCount</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Daily</schedule><script><![CDATA[answer = JSON.stringify(conversationCount());

function conversationCount() {
    var result = {};
    if (!GlideTableDescriptor.isValid('sys_cs_conversation')) {
      return result;
    }
    var ga = new GlideAggregate('sys_cs_conversation');
    ga.addAggregate('COUNT', 'state');
    ga.query();

    var count = 0;
    var stateCount = 0;
    while (ga.next()) {
      stateCount = parseInt(ga.getAggregate('COUNT', 'state'));
      result[ga.state] = stateCount;
      count += stateCount;
    }
    result.count = count;
    return result;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-08-24 19:25:02</sys_created_on><sys_id>49357655db74030066e778b5ae9619d7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEFN1000501</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_49357655db74030066e778b5ae9619d7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Usage</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000408</definition_id><description>Maximum transactions in last 12 months for all scopes</description><exec_time_threshold>5000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>outbound_usage_metrics_max_all</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>false</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Monthly</schedule><script><![CDATA[var aggregator = new OutboundUsageMetricsAggregator();
var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', false);
var maxCount = 0;
while (sums.next()) {  
  var currentCount = parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'agg_value'));
  if(currentCount > maxCount) 
    maxCount = currentCount;
}
answer = maxCount;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-08-17 00:14:12</sys_created_on><sys_id>b17a2e36e7a0030007a64caac2f6a9df</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000408</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_b17a2e36e7a0030007a64caac2f6a9df</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-25 14:41:02</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="usageanalytics_count_cfg"><usageanalytics_count_cfg action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><count_type>Licensing</count_type><definition_id>DEF1000213</definition_id><description>Number of unique nodes that Orchestration has run an activity on</description><exec_time_threshold>300000</exec_time_threshold><license_model>0</license_model><name>UniqueNodesOrchestrated</name><overridden>false</overridden><query/><reportable>true</reportable><run_scope>global</run_scope><schedule>Daily</schedule><script><![CDATA[var rowCount = 0;
var value='';
var gra = new GlideAggregate('orch_execution');
if (gra.isValid()) {
  gra.addAggregate('COUNT(distinct', 'node_id');
  gra.addQuery('sys_updated_on', '>=', gs.daysAgoStart(365));
  gra.query();
  if (gra.next())
  rowCount = gra.getRowCount();
}
else {
  value='No Table';
}

answer = rowCount;]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-08-04 23:11:02</sys_created_on><sys_id>34d83c2dcb012200467d3682634c9ca0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000213</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_34d83c2dcb012200467d3682634c9ca0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-11 23:51:46</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>

count = count - sampCount;

var sums = aggregator.getTransactionCountByMonth('sys_hub_step_instance', true);
var maxCount = 0;
while (sums.next()) {  
  var currentCount = parseInt(sums.getAggregate('SUM', 'agg_value'));
  if(currentCount > maxCount) 
    maxCount = currentCount;
}
answer = maxCount;


]]></script><sys_class_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-08-10 00:09:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>d736a2a4e720030007a64caac2f6a93a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>18</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DEF1000401</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Usage Analytics" source="com.glide.usageanalytics">9ef891387420330078509adcc48c8705</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>usageanalytics_count_cfg_d736a2a4e720030007a64caac2f6a93a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>developer.program@snc</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-05-25 14:41:03</sys_updated_on></usageanalytics_count_cfg></record_update>
